                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "Once per day as a full action while outdoors and in line of sight of a flying allied starship, an Overwatch captain can coordinate an exceptionally accurate air strike against an outdoor area with a 20-foot radius at a range of 1 mile. At the beginning of the captain\u2019s next turn, the allied starship fires, dealing 10d8 fire and piercing damage to anything in the area. Creatures take half damage with a successful Reflex save (DC 12 + 1/2 the captain\u2019s CR).",
